com.example.preemptiveoop.trial.model

Class GenericTrial

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.preemptiveoop.trial.model.GenericTrial
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BinomialTrial, CountTrial, MeasurementTrial, NonNegativeTrial

    public class GenericTrial
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The GenericTrial class is a Firestore compatible class used as a intermedium for reading/writing trial data to Firestore. It contains conversion methods for other specific trial types.
